  "texts": [
    "Blank spaces represent data that were not originally collected.",
    "Regarding wearable sensors, all sensor data are accessible, except for eye-tracking data from participants labeled Sub05, Sub06, and Sub08.",
    "For these participants, the eye-tracking camera was either broken, the gaze data were missing, or the gaze data were not collected; therefore, these data were excluded from the available data.",
    "Also, some videos were not recorded owing to program interruption during data collection.",
    "In preparation for this, multiple cameras were used to record concurrently to minimize missing annotation data."
